{"id":594122,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/【麻辣总局】境外维权说台独-境内报警说上访/","date":"2018-08-27T02:57:00Z","modified":"2018-08-27T02:57:00Z","title":"【麻辣总局】境外维权说台独 境内报警说上访","content":"<p>8月24日，一名台湾画师被人盗图放淘宝店铺上销售，维权无门，于是找到朋友向卖家“报信”说自己是台独，对方立即将作品下架。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://t.co/hHWyc7YOfb\">https://t.co/hHWyc7YOfb</a><br />台灣繪師發現自己的作品被盜圖，在淘寶上被做成文具<br />↓<br />淘寶檢舉機制根本沒用<br />↓<br />跑去跟盜用者說原作是台獨<br />↓<br />盜用者十分鐘內下架 ←目前在這裡</p>\n<p>&mdash; 逃避現實的生物 (@EscapeLion) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EscapeLion/status/1033643271799562241?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 26, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2H7HkcStkhXxpeUW3yMwUs.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-594123\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2H7HkcStkhXxpeUW3yMwUs.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2H7HkcStkhXxpeUW3yMwUs.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2H7HkcStkhXxpeUW3yMwUs-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2H7HkcStkhXxpeUW3yMwUs-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2H7HkcStkhXxpeUW3yMwUs-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/5P4cLqFh16bs3mH9lqO8nc.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-594124\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/5P4cLqFh16bs3mH9lqO8nc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/5P4cLqFh16bs3mH9lqO8nc.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/5P4cLqFh16bs3mH9lqO8nc-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/5P4cLqFh16b